#: ../../source/reference/learn/generated/maxframe.learn.cluster.KMeans.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.learn.cluster.KMeans"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.cluster._kmeans.KMeans:1 of
msgid "K-Means clustering."
msgstr "K-均值聚类。"

#: maxframe.learn.cluster._kmeans.KMeans:3 of
msgid "Read more in the :ref:`User Guide <k_means>`."
msgstr "更多信息请参阅 :ref:`用户指南 <k_means>`。"

#: ../../source/reference/learn/generated/maxframe.learn.cluster.KMeans.rst
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.cluster._kmeans.KMeans:5 of
msgid ""
"The number of clusters to form as well as the number of centroids to "
"generate."
msgstr "要形成的聚类数量以及要生成的质心数量。"

#: maxframe.learn.cluster._kmeans.KMeans:8 of
msgid ""
"Method for initialization, defaults to 'k-means||':  'k-means++' : "
"selects initial cluster centers for k-mean clustering in a smart way to "
"speed up convergence. See section Notes in k_init for more details.  "
"'k-means||': scalable k-means++.  'random': choose k observations (rows) "
"at random from data for the initial centroids.  If a tensor is passed, it"
" should be of shape (n_clusters, n_features) and gives the initial "
"centers."
msgstr ""
"初始化方法，默认为 'k-means||'：  'k-means++' : 以一种智能的方式选择初始"
"聚类中心，以加速收敛。详见 k_init 中的说明。  'k-means||': 可扩展的 k-"
"means++。  'random': 从数据中随机选择 k 个观测（行）作为初始质心。  如果"
"传递的是张量，则其形状应为 (n_clusters, n_features)，并给出初始中心。"

#: maxframe.learn.cluster._kmeans.KMeans:8 of
msgid "Method for initialization, defaults to 'k-means||':"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.cluster._kmeans.KMeans:10 of
msgid ""
"'k-means++' : selects initial cluster centers for k-mean clustering in a "
"smart way to speed up convergence. See section Notes in k_init for more "
"details."
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.cluster._kmeans.KMeans:14 of
msgid "'k-means||': scalable k-means++."
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.cluster._kmeans.KMeans:16 of
msgid ""
"'random': choose k observations (rows) at random from data for the "
"initial centroids."
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.cluster._kmeans.KMeans:19 of
msgid ""
"If a tensor is passed, it should be of shape (n_clusters, n_features) and"
" gives the initial centers."
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.cluster._kmeans.KMeans:22 of
msgid ""
"Number of time the k-means algorithm will be run with different centroid "
"seeds. The final results will be the best output of n_init consecutive "
"runs in terms of inertia."
msgstr ""
"k-means 算法将使用不同的质心种子运行的次数。最终结果将是 n_init 次连续"
"运行中惯性最小的最佳输出。"

#: maxframe.learn.cluster._kmeans.KMeans:26 of
msgid "Maximum number of iterations of the k-means algorithm for a single run."
msgstr "单次运行中 k-means 算法的最大迭代次数。"

#: maxframe.learn.cluster._kmeans.KMeans:29 of
msgid "Relative tolerance with regards to inertia to declare convergence."
msgstr "相对于惯性的收敛判断相对容差。"

#: maxframe.learn.cluster._kmeans.KMeans:31 of
msgid "Verbosity mode."
msgstr "详细模式。"

#: maxframe.learn.cluster._kmeans.KMeans:33 of
msgid ""
"Determines random number generation for centroid initialization. Use an "
"int to make the randomness deterministic. See :term:`Glossary "
"<random_state>`."
msgstr ""
"确定质心初始化的随机数生成方式。使用整数可使随机性变为确定性的。详见 :"
"term:`术语表 <random_state>`。"

#: maxframe.learn.cluster._kmeans.KMeans:37 of
msgid ""
"When pre-computing distances it is more numerically accurate to center "
"the data first.  If copy_x is True (default), then the original data is "
"not modified, ensuring X is C-contiguous.  If False, the original data is"
" modified, and put back before the function returns, but small numerical "
"differences may be introduced by subtracting and then adding the data "
"mean, in this case it will also not ensure that data is C-contiguous "
"which may cause a significant slowdown."
msgstr ""
"在预先计算距离时，首先将数据居中会更精确。如果 copy_x 为 True（默认），则"
"原始数据不会被修改，以确保 X 是 C 连续的。如果为 False，则原始数据会被"
"修改，并在函数返回前恢复，但减去并加上数据均值可能会引入微小的数值差异，"
"在这种情况下也无法确保数据是 C 连续的，这可能导致显著的性能下降。"

#: maxframe.learn.cluster._kmeans.KMeans:45 of
msgid ""
"K-means algorithm to use. The classical EM-style algorithm is \"full\". "
"The \"elkan\" variation is more efficient by using the triangle "
"inequality, but currently doesn't support sparse data. \"auto\" chooses "
"\"elkan\" for dense data and \"full\" for sparse data."
msgstr ""
"使用的 K-means 算法。经典 EM 风格的算法是 \"full\"。\"elkan\" 变体通过"
"使用三角不等式更高效，但目前不支持稀疏数据。\"auto\" 会为密集数据选择 \""
"elkan\"，为稀疏数据选择 \"full\"。"

#: maxframe.learn.cluster._kmeans.KMeans:50 of
msgid "Only work for kmeans||, used in each iteration in kmeans||."
msgstr "仅适用于 kmeans||，在每次 kmeans|| 迭代中使用。"

#: maxframe.learn.cluster._kmeans.KMeans:52 of
msgid "Only work for kmeans||, indicates how may iterations required."
msgstr "仅适用于 kmeans||，表示需要多少次迭代。"

#: maxframe.learn.cluster._kmeans.KMeans:57 of
msgid ""
"Coordinates of cluster centers. If the algorithm stops before fully "
"converging (see ``tol`` and ``max_iter``), these will not be consistent "
"with ``labels_``."
msgstr ""
"聚类中心的坐标。如果算法在完全收敛之前停止（见 ``tol`` 和 ``max_iter``）"
"，这些将与 ``labels_`` 不一致。"

#: maxframe.learn.cluster._kmeans.KMeans of
msgid "type"
msgstr "类型"

#: maxframe.learn.cluster._kmeans.KMeans:61 of
msgid "tensor of shape (n_clusters, n_features)"
msgstr "形状为 (n_clusters, n_features) 的张量"

#: maxframe.learn.cluster._kmeans.KMeans:65 of
msgid "Labels of each point"
msgstr "每个点的标签"

#: maxframe.learn.cluster._kmeans.KMeans:67 of
msgid "tensor of shape (n_samples,)"
msgstr "形状为 (n_samples,) 的张量"

#: maxframe.learn.cluster._kmeans.KMeans:71 of
msgid "Sum of squared distances of samples to their closest cluster center."
msgstr "样本到其最近聚类中心的平方距离之和。"

#: maxframe.learn.cluster._kmeans.KMeans:73 of
msgid "float"
msgstr "浮点数"

#: maxframe.learn.cluster._kmeans.KMeans:77 of
msgid "Number of iterations run."
msgstr "运行的迭代次数。"

#: maxframe.learn.cluster._kmeans.KMeans:79 of
msgid "int"
msgstr "整数"

#: maxframe.learn.cluster._kmeans.KMeans:83 of
msgid ":py:obj:`MiniBatchKMeans`"
msgstr "MiniBatchKMeans"

#: maxframe.learn.cluster._kmeans.KMeans:84 of
msgid ""
"Alternative online implementation that does incremental updates of the "
"centers positions using mini-batches. For large scale learning (say "
"n_samples > 10k) MiniBatchKMeans is probably much faster than the default"
" batch implementation."
msgstr ""
"使用小批量进行中心位置增量更新的替代在线实现。对于大规模学习（例如 n_"
"samples > 10k），MiniBatchKMeans 可能比默认的批量实现快得多。"

#: maxframe.learn.cluster._kmeans.KMeans:87 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.cluster._kmeans.KMeans:88 of
msgid "The k-means problem is solved using either Lloyd's or Elkan's algorithm."
msgstr "k-means 问题通过 Lloyd 或 Elkan 算法解决。"

#: maxframe.learn.cluster._kmeans.KMeans:90 of
msgid ""
"The average complexity is given by O(k n T), were n is the number of "
"samples and T is the number of iteration."
msgstr "平均复杂度为 O(k n T)，其中 n 是样本数量，T 是迭代次数。"

#: maxframe.learn.cluster._kmeans.KMeans:93 of
msgid ""
"The worst case complexity is given by O(n^(k+2/p)) with n = n_samples, p "
"= n_features. (D. Arthur and S. Vassilvitskii, 'How slow is the k-means "
"method?' SoCG2006)"
msgstr ""
"最坏情况下的复杂度为 O(n^(k+2/p))，其中 n = n_samples，p = n_features。（"
"D. Arthur 和 S. Vassilvitskii，《k-means 方法有多慢？》，SoCG2006）"

#: maxframe.learn.cluster._kmeans.KMeans:97 of
msgid ""
"In practice, the k-means algorithm is very fast (one of the fastest "
"clustering algorithms available), but it falls in local minima. That's "
"why it can be useful to restart it several times."
msgstr ""
"在实际应用中，k-means 算法非常快（是可用的最快聚类算法之一），但它会陷入"
"局部最小值。这就是为什么多次重启它可能会有帮助。"

#: maxframe.learn.cluster._kmeans.KMeans:101 of
msgid ""
"If the algorithm stops before fully converging (because of ``tol`` or "
"``max_iter``), ``labels_`` and ``cluster_centers_`` will not be "
"consistent, i.e. the ``cluster_centers_`` will not be the means of the "
"points in each cluster. Also, the estimator will reassign ``labels_`` "
"after the last iteration to make ``labels_`` consistent with ``predict`` "
"on the training set."
msgstr ""
"如果算法在完全收敛之前停止（由于 ``tol`` 或 ``max_iter``），``labels_`` "
"和 ``cluster_centers_`` 将不一致，即 ``cluster_centers_`` 不会是每个聚类"
"中点的均值。此外，估计器将在最后一次迭代后重新分配 ``labels_``，以使 ``"
"labels_`` 与训练集上的 ``predict`` 保持一致。"

